description: The VictoryShares US 500 Volatility Wtd ETF offers exposure to large-cap US stocks, without subjecting investors to the inherent limitations of traditional market-cap weighting. It seeks to provide investment results that track the performance of the Nasdaq Victory US Large Cap 500 Volatility Weighted Index before fees and expenses. Volatility Weighting Methodology Combines fundamental criteria and volatility weighting in an effort to outperform traditional cap-weighted indexing strategies.
name: VictoryShares US 500 Volatility Wtd ETF
